       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. HELLO-WORLD.
       AUTHOR. TEST-AUTHOR.

       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-MESSAGE       PIC X(30) VALUE "HELLO, WORLD!".
       01  WS-COUNTER       PIC 9(3)  VALUE 0.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       MAIN-PARAGRAPH.
           DISPLAY WS-MESSAGE
           ADD 1 TO WS-COUNTER
           DISPLAY "COUNTER: " WS-COUNTER
           STOP RUN.
